ss=md-nav data-md-level=1 aria-labelledby=__nav_7_label aria-expanded=false> <label class=md-nav__title for=__nav_7> <span class="md-nav__icon md-icon"></span> Community </label> <ul class=md-nav__list data-md-scrollfix> <li class=md-nav__item> <a href=community/faq/ class=md-nav__link> <span class=md-ellipsis> FAQ </span> </a> </li> <li class=md-nav__item> <a href=community/contributing/ class=md-nav__link> <span class=md-ellipsis> Contributing </span> </a> </li> <li class=md-nav__item> <a href=community/code-of-conduct/ class=md-nav__link> <span class=md-ellipsis> Code of Conduct </span> </a> </li> <li class=md-nav__item> <a href=community/security/ class=md-nav__link> <span class=md-ellipsis> Security </span> </a> </li> <li class=md-nav__item> <a href=community/support/ class=md-nav__link> <span class=md-ellipsis> Support </span> </a> </li> <li class=md-nav__item> <a href=community/contact-us/ class=md-nav__link> <span class=md-ellipsis> Contact us </span> </a> </li> </ul> </nav> </li> </ul> </nav> </div> </div> </div> <div class="md-sidebar md-sidebar--secondary" data-md-component=sidebar data-md-type=toc> <div class=md-sidebar__scrollwrap> <div class=md-sidebar__inner> <nav class="md-nav md-nav--secondary" aria-label="Table of contents"> <label class=md-nav__title for=__toc> <span class="md-nav__icon md-icon"></span> Table of contents </label> <ul class=md-nav__list data-md-component=toc data-md-scrollfix> <li class=md-nav__item> <a href=#key-capabilities class=md-nav__link> <span class=md-ellipsis> 🚀 Key Capabilities </span> </a> </li> <li class=md-nav__item> <a href=#where-to-start class=md-nav__link> <span class=md-ellipsis> 🧭 Where to Start </span> </a> </li> <li class=md-nav__item> <a href=#sdks class=md-nav__link> <span class=md-ellipsis> 🛠 SDKs </span> </a> </li> <li class=md-nav__item> <a href=#contribute class=md-nav__link> <span class=md-ellipsis> 🤝 Contribute </span> </a> </li> <li class=md-nav__item> <a href=#learn-more class=md-nav__link> <span class=md-ellipsis> 📚 Learn More </span> </a> </li> <li class=md-nav__item> <a href=#community-support class=md-nav__link> <span class=md-ellipsis> 💬 Community &amp; Support </span> </a> </li> </ul> </nav> </div> </div> </div> <div class=md-content data-md-component=content> <article class="md-content__inner md-typeset"> <p align=center> <img src=assets/images/jenticDocsBanner.png alt="Jentic GitHub Banner" style="max-width: 100%; border-radius: 10px;"> </p> <div align=center> <h3> <a href=guides/mcp/remote-mcp><strong>MCP Integrations</strong></a> · <a href=getting-started/api-scoring><strong>API AI-Readiness Scoring</strong></a> · <a href=getting-started/arazzo-runner><strong>Arazzo Runner</strong></a> · <a href=getting-started/api-search><strong>Jentic API Search</strong></a> · <a href=getting-started/standard-agent><strong>Standard Agent</strong></a> </h3> <br> <a href=https://discord.gg/xRResx3ZNW><img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/Discord-Join%20Chat-5865F2?logo=discord&logoColor=white" alt="Join us on Discord"></a> <a href=https://www.linkedin.com/company/jentic/ target=_blank> <img src="https://custom-icon-badges.demolab.com/badge/LinkedIn-0A66C2?logo=linkedin-white&logoColor=fff" alt="Follow on LinkedIn"></a> <a href=https://bsky.app/profile/jentic.bsky.social target=_blank> <img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/Bluesky-1DA1F2?logo=bluesky&logoColor=white" alt="Follow on Bluesky"></a> <a href=https://pypi.python.org/pypi/arazzo-runner><img src="https://img.shields.io/pypi/dm/arazzo-runner?logo=python&logoColor=white&label=pypi%20arazzorunner&color=blue" alt="Arazzo Runner Python package on PyPI"></a> <a href=https://github.com/jentic/jentic-public-apis/graphs/commit-activity><img src="https://img.shields.io/github/commit-activity/m/jentic/jentic-public-apis?color=orange" alt="Monthly commits"></a> <a href=https://github.com/jentic/jentic-public-apis><img src="https://img.shields.io/github/stars/jentic/jentic-public-apis?style=social" alt="GitHub stars"></a> </div> <hr> <h1 id=welcome-to-jentic>Welcome to Jentic<a class=headerlink href=#welcome-to-jentic title="Permanent link">&para;</a></h1> <p><strong>One platform for all your agent capabilities — open, secure, and reliable.</strong></p> <p>Jentic enables AI agents to dynamically discover and execute APIs and workflows through a standards-based, open-source catalog.<br> With <strong>managed authentication</strong>, <strong>unified permissions</strong>, and <strong>observability</strong>, your agents become more capable, safer, and easier to operate at scale.</p> <blockquote> <p><strong>Quickstart:</strong> Ready to run your first workflow? → <a href=getting-started/quickstart>Quickstart guide</a></p> </blockquote> <hr> <h2 id=key-capabilities>🚀 Key Capabilities<a class=headerlink href=#key-capabilities title="Permanent link">&para;</a></h2> <ul> <li><strong>6,000+ APIs, 2,000+ workflows</strong> — all agent-ready and described in open standards (<strong>OpenAPI</strong>, <strong>Arazzo</strong>, <strong>MCP</strong>).</li> <li><strong>Just-in-Time Tooling (JITT)</strong> — load tools on-demand for clarity and reliability.</li> <li><strong>Managed authentication &amp; access control</strong> — no secrets in prompts or client code.</li> <li><strong>Workflow learning loop</strong> — agents get smarter with every call.</li> <li><strong>API AI-Readiness Scoring</strong> — grade any OpenAPI document against <a href=reference/api-readiness-framework/overview/ >Jentic's API AI-Readiness Framework</a> via CLI, GitHub Action, agent skill, or web UI.</li> <li><strong>Open source, open standards</strong> — portable, vendor-neutral, community-driven.</li> </ul> <p>Learn more in <a href=concepts/business-agents>Business Agents</a>.</p> <hr> <h2 id=where-to-start>🧭 Where to Start<a class=headerlink href=#where-to-start title="Permanent link">&para;</a></h2> <ol> <li><strong><a href=getting-started/quickstart>Quickstart</a></strong> – run your first workflow in minutes. </li> <li><strong><a href=guides/mcp/remote-mcp>MCP Integrations</a></strong> – connect Jentic to Cursor, Windsurf, Claude Desktop, ChatGPT, VS Code. </li> <li><strong><a href=getting-started/arazzo-runner>Arazzo Runner</a></strong> – execute workflows from the CLI or Python. </li> <li><strong><a href=getting-started/api-search>API Search</a></strong> – explore the catalog in your browser.</li> <li><strong><a href=getting-started/api-scoring>API Scoring</a></strong> – grade your OpenAPI documents for AI-readiness.</li> <li><strong><a href=getting-started/standard-agent>Standard Agent</a></strong> – modular agent framework with Jentic tools built-in.</li> </ol> <hr> <h2 id=sdks>🛠 SDKs<a class=headerlink href=#sdks title="Permanent link">&para;</a></h2> <ul> <li><strong><a href=reference/sdks/python>Python SDK</a></strong> – search, load, execute, and integrate tools into your agents.</li> <li><strong><a href=reference/sdks/typescript>TypeScript SDK</a></strong> – <em>not yet available</em>; <a href=https://github.com/jentic/jentic-public-apis/issues>request it here</a>.</li> </ul> <hr> <h2 id=contribute>🤝 Contribute<a class=headerlink href=#contribute title="Permanent link">&para;</a></h2> <p>Jentic is <strong>open-source</strong> and thrives on community input. You can:</p> <ul> <li><a href=guides/add-api-integration>Add API Integrations</a> – submit OpenAPI Documents or Descriptions.</li> <li><a href=guides/create-agent-workflows>Create Agent Workflows</a> – define reusable business logic.</li> <li><a href=community/contributing>Contribute to Jentic Public APIs</a> – improve the catalog and tooling.</li> </ul> <p>For more ways to help, see our <a href=community/faq>FAQ</a> and join us on <a href=https://discord.gg/xRResx3ZNW>Discord</a>.</p> <hr> <h2 id=learn-more>📚 Learn More<a class=headerlink href=#learn-more title="Permanent link">&para;</a></h2> <ul> <li><strong><a href=concepts/business-agents>Business Agents</a></strong> – the agent pattern Jentic is built for.</li> <li><strong><a href=getting-started/api-scoring>API AI-Readiness Scoring</a></strong> – check how ready your APIs are for agent consumption.</li> <li><strong><a href=https://github.com/jentic/jentic-public-apis>Jentic Public APIs</a></strong> – open, AI-ready API &amp; workflow catalog.</li> <li><strong><a href=https://github.com/jentic/arazzo-engine>Arazzo</a></strong> – open standard for declarative workflows.</li> </ul> <hr> <h2 id=community-support>💬 Community &amp; Support<a class=headerlink href=#community-support title="Permanent link">&para;</a></h2> <ul> <li><strong>Discord:</strong> <a href=https://discord.gg/xRResx3ZNW>Join the discussion</a> </li> <li><strong>GitHub:</strong> <a href=https://github.com/jentic/jentic-public-apis/discussions>Discussions</a> | <a href=https://github.com/jentic/jentic-public-apis/issues>Issues</a> </li> <li><strong>LinkedIn:</strong> <a href=https://www.linkedin.com/company/jentic/ >Jentic</a></li> </ul> <hr> <p align=center> <a href=getting-started/quickstart><strong>Get Started →</strong></a> </p> <aside class=md-source-file> <span class=md-source-file__fact> <span class=md-icon title="Last update"> <svg xmlns=http://www.w3.org/2000/svg viewbox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M21 13.1c-.1 0-.3.1-.4.2l-1 1 2.1 2.1 1-1c.2-.2.2-.6 0-.8l-1.3-1.3c-.1-.1-.2-.2-.4-.2m-1.9 1.8-6.1 6V23h2.1l6.1-6.1zM12.5 7v5.2l4 2.4-1 1L11 13V7zM11 21.9c-5.1-.5-9-4.8-9-9.9C2 6.5 6.5 2 12 2c5.3 0 9.6 4.1 10 9.3-.3-.1-.6-.2-1-.2s-.7.1-1 .2C19.6 7.2 16.2 4 12 4c-4.4 0-8 3.6-8 8 0 4.1 3.1 7.5 7.1 7.9l-.1.2z"/></svg> </span> <span class="git-revision-date-localized-plugin git-revision-date-localized-plugin-date" title="July 20, 2026 10:01:59 UTC">July 20, 2026</span> </span> <span class=md-source-file__fact> <span class=md-icon title=Created> <svg xmlns=http://www.w3.org/2000/svg viewbox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M14.47 15.08 11 13V7h1.5v5.25l3.08 1.83c-.41.28-.79.62-1.11 1m-1.39 4.84c-.36.05-.71.08-1.08.08-4.42 0-8-3.58-8-8s3.58-8 8-8 8 3.58 8 8c0 .37-.03.72-.08 1.08.69